title: Silicon Valley IPO market boom winding down, data shows
text: San Fransisco (Heather Somerville, Reuters) – Last year, many tech IPOs enjoyed soaring valuations in their Wall Street debut, raining cash on the companies and their investors and boosting concerns about another Silicon Valley bubble.
